# (2) : brightness (0-100)
*INCREASE*BRIGHTNESS* (*)==jv_pg_yl_command "brightness" (1) 100
*DECREASE*BRIGHTNESS* (*)==jv_pg_yl_command "brightness" (1) 30
*CHANGE*BRIGHTNESS* (*) (*)==jv_pg_yl_command "brightness" (1) (2)


